headline: Cross Ocean Partners and Lincoln Property Company Acquire 409,000-SF Office Campus in Needham, Massachusetts
summary: NEEDHAM, Mass., December 17, 2025--Cross Ocean Partners ("Cross Ocean"), a global asset management platform focused on special situations, credit and hard asset investments, and Lincoln Property Company ("Lincoln"), a global, full-service real estate firm, today announced the acquisition of a trophy office campus in Needham, Massachusetts for $132 million.

headline: How Is BXP, Inc.'s Stock Performance Compared to Other REIT Stocks?
summary: BXP, Inc. has underperformed the REIT industry over the past year, but analysts are cautiously optimistic about the stock’s prospects.
